name: Monday Dreaming
description:
Introducing our cat, Suzuki the orange cat. What he love most is taking a day nap. Sometimes I wish I was him, just dozing off all day, "leyeh-leyeh" is his way of life. He look harmless but he's the best hunter of it's kind, mice, small bird, chameleon, lizzard, every morning we found dead something-something on our backyard.

*leyeh-leyeh (javanese language: to chillin' out laying on a flat surfaces)

0:08 secs 1080x1080p
animated drawings + music illustration.
